<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head') %>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

        <div class="container" style="padding-top: 150px; padding-bottom: 100px; min-height: 80vh;">
            <div
                style="max-width: 450px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; padding: 3rem; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
                    <div
                        style="width: 70px; height: 70px; background: var(--color-primary); color: white; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem; font-size: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                        <i class="fas fa-key"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h1 style="font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 700; color: #333; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">비밀번호 변경</h1>
                    <p style="color: #666;">계정을 안전하게 보호하기 위해<br>주기적으로 비밀번호를 변경해 주세요.</p>
                </div>

                <form action="/admin/change-password" method="POST">
                    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
                        <label
                            style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; font-weight: 600; color: #444; font-size: 0.95rem;">현재
                            비밀번호</label>
                        <input type="password" name="currentPassword" required
                            style="width: 100%; padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 12px; background: #fdfdfd; transition: all 0.3s;"
                            placeholder="현재 비밀번호를 입력하세요">
                    </div>

                    <div style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-top: 1px solid #f5f5f5; padding-top: 1.5rem;">
                        <label
                            style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; font-weight: 600; color: #444; font-size: 0.95rem;">새
                            비밀번호</label>
                        <input type="password" name="newPassword" required
                            style="width: 100%; padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 12px; background: #fdfdfd; transition: all 0.3s;"
                            placeholder="새 비밀번호 입력">
                    </div>

                    <div style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">
                        <label
                            style="display: block; margin-bottom: 0.6rem; font-weight: 600; color: #444; font-size: 0.95rem;">새
                            비밀번호 확인</label>
                        <input type="password" name="confirmPassword" required
                            style="width: 100%; padding: 1rem; border: 1px solid #eee; border-radius: 12px; background: #fdfdfd; transition: all 0.3s;"
                            placeholder="새 비밀번호 다시 입력">
                    </div>

                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary"
                        style="width: 100%; padding: 1.1rem; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 0.8rem; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> 비밀번호 변경하기
                    </button>

                    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                        <a href="javascript:history.back()"
                            style="color: #999; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem;">
                            <i class="fas fa-times"></i> 취소하고 돌아가기
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>

        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
            <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>

</html>